Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}我想我們一定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:13.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,0)}從太古時代起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:17.04,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就相互吸引著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:20.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是命運的呼喚
